\lim_{x\to3}\frac{x^2-8x+15}{x-3}&=\lim_{x\to3}\frac{(x-5)(x-3)}{x-3}&&\text{Indeterminate $\frac{0}{0}$ form}
&=\lim_{x\to3}(x-5)&&\text{Limit Law A7}
&=\lim_{x\to3}x-\lim_{x\to3}5&&\text{Limit Law A2}
&=3-5&&\text{Limit Laws R1 and R2}
&=-2
